(35, 22, 0, 34, 0, 0, 'AQUAMED 胎盘素活肤面膜', 45, 40.5, 45, 0, 10, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:&apos;lucida Grande&apos;, Verdana, &apos;Microsoft YaHei&apos;;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\n	<span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="color:#FF0066;font-family:宋体;font-size:27px;font-weight:bold;line-height:39px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">产品说明：</span>12</span><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:微软雅黑;">年台湾医美专用品牌<span>AQUAMED</span>，源于法文<span>AQUA-</span>“具有理疗效果的水<span>”</span>，是少数通过<span>GMP</span>国际药品生产质量管理规范，<span>ISO<span>22716</span></span>化妆品行业安全生产规范认证的护肤产品，以天然、安全、高效，成为台湾药房和医疗机构专售的顶级医疗美肤品牌。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:&apos;lucida Grande&apos;, Verdana, &apos;Microsoft YaHei&apos;;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\n	<span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:微软雅黑;">采用台湾生物科学技术，无添加提炼胎盘萃取物<span style="color:red;">25%</span>（<span>Placenta extract</span>）高分子玻尿酸 <span style="color:red;">15%</span><span>(Hyalo-Oligo) </span>植物性胶原蛋白<span style="color:red;">10%</span>（<span>r-PGA</span>）等多重医疗美容滋养精华，给肌肤比传统面膜更高的吸收能力，迅速消除暗沉，抑黑美白，焕活新生。不含化学激素、增稠剂，以天然粘性成分，提高角质层保水度，高效解决皮肤干皱。富含多种生长因子和修护因子，抚平细纹，长效维持肌肤细嫩光泽，延缓衰老。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:&apos;lucida Grande&apos;, Verdana, &apos;Microsoft YaHei&apos;;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\n	<span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:微软雅黑;">创新选用<span>Sontara</span>美国<span>100%</span>植物天丝棉面膜，提升肌触感与吸水力，有效导入滋养因子，让日常护肤达到医学美容治疗的效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:&apos;lucida Grande&apos;, Verdana, &apos;Microsoft YaHei&apos;;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\n	<span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:微软雅黑;">\n	<p style="margin-left:0in;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0in;background-color:#FFFFFF;vertical-align:baseline;">\n		<span style="font-size:20pt;font-family:宋体;color:#FF0066;font-weight:bold;">产品功效：</span><span style="font-size:20pt;font-family:宋体;">生化技术萃取提炼多重滋养精华，给与肌肤比传统面膜更高的吸收能力，将水分锁在肌肤底层、迅速消除暗沉、抚平细纹、使脸色看起来水润、弹性有光泽、减缓老化。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p style="margin-left:0in;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0in;background-color:#FFFFFF;vertical-align:baseline;">\n		<span style="font-size:20pt;font-family:宋体;color:#FF0066;font-weight:bold;">使用说明：</span><span style="font-size:20pt;font-family:宋体;">洗净肌肤后，取出胎盘素活肤面膜紧密贴于全脸上约15-20分钟，待精华液被吸收后，即可取下。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p style="margin-left:0in;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0in;background-color:#FFFFFF;vertical-align:baseline;">\n		<span style="font-size:20pt;font-family:宋体;"><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/f/e/7/5/557546b48833e.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/8/7/e/557546c0404f0.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/d/b/3/6/557546cd91156.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/4/b/8/b/557546dda4f60.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/a/f/5/557546eba5a93.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/3/9/8/2/557546fb20eb5.jpg" alt="" /><br />\n</span>\n	</p>\n<br />\n</span>\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '面膜 保湿 美白 ', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/f/4/1/5/thumb_5575439ad6c85.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433749328, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(36, 22, 0, 33, 0, 0, '芷伊兰美颜系列氨基酸洁颜慕斯 150ml', 260, 234, 260, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>产品说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	氨基酸洁肤因子，柔细的泡沫能平衡多余油脂并清除污垢及老旧角质，生理性PH值，温和不刺激，使用后清爽舒适，不紧绷，保持肌肤的水份。天天使用可改善粉刺阻塞，促进毛孔畅通。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>使用说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	轻按2-3下，将按出的泡沫直接涂抹于打湿的脸庞，轻轻按摩全脸，然后用水清洗。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/7/d/9/a/55754778d62bf.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/f/2/5/b/5575478692160.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/4/9/a/2/5575478e05415.jpg" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '洁面、清洁', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/7/d/a/5/thumb_5575472a2eb73.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433749398, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(37, 22, 0, 33, 0, 0, '芷伊兰美颜系列净肤洁面凝露', 128, 115, 128, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>产品说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	温和舒适的洁净配方，调节肌肤表面微生物数量和皮肤油脂过度分泌，降低刺激。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>使用说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	取适量于手心，用清水揉出泡沫，轻柔按摩于脸部，然后以清水洗净即可。<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/3/2/1/f/557548ba3fb22.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/0/f/3/9/557548cb1e132.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/4/9/7/3/557548e11f00c.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/c/e/d/0/557548fb4a119.jpg" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '洁面、清洁', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/c/e/3/b/thumb_5575485f5a613.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433749762, 0, 1000, 'fixed', '0.00', '0', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(38, 22, 0, 34, 0, 0, '兰花水嫩精华面膜', 45, 40.5, 45, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：精细的生化技术萃取提炼的兰花与植物多重滋养精华、给予肌肤比传统面膜更高的吸收及保湿与滋润能力，只需15分钟，将水分锁在肌肤底层、让肌肤散发透亮水嫩自然光泽,迅速消除暗沉、抚平细纹、增进肌肤的紧致与弹力,\n让肌肤呈现年轻与青春的活力.\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：清洁后,\n撕开铝箔袋，取下珍珠纸、将面膜布敷于脸上，15分钟取下即可.\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/5/f/d/6/557548f7e6546.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/f/1/e/f/557549046527e.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/b/a/3/f/5575490e6964a.JPG" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '面膜 补水 美白', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/3/7/5/5/thumb_5575482239488.JPG', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433749783, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(39, 22, 0, 34, 0, 0, '鑚美姬专业级保湿锁水面膜', 45, 40.5, 45, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：内含高效天然保湿因子，可滋润柔软肌肤并增加肌肤含水量及弹性，使肌肤光滑柔软有光泽。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：清洁脸部后，取出面膜敷于脸部10-15分，卸下面膜后接续使用钻美姬保养系列，面膜请勿重复使用。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/a/5/f/55754a1db9809.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/6/2/9/e/55754a2bf352c.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/b/e/b/b/55754a367210b.JPG" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '面膜 保湿 锁水 美白 ', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/3/a/7/8/thumb_557549ae9ded6.JPG', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433750075, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(40, 22, 0, 33, 0, 0, '芷伊兰美颜系列玫瑰氨基酸洁面凝露  120ml', 90, 81, 90, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>产品说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	针对敏感性等问题肤质做好最基础的清洁工作，采用最天然的氨基酸温和配方，能温和且深层洗净油垢、角质及残妆。搭配玫瑰精露，能使受损的皮肤加速复原且明亮肤质，使用后肌肤看起来细致、水嫩、弹性有光泽。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>使用说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	取适量于手心，用清水揉出泡沫，轻柔按摩于脸部，然后以清水洗净即可。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/e/d/5/7/55754a656c6ad.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/0/5/3/55754a749704e.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/9/e/0/55754a85385a3.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/3/5/2/9/55754a92f3da7.jpg" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '洁面、清洁', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/c/3/0/thumb_55754a0d24074.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433750168, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(41, 22, 0, 36, 0, 0, '芷伊兰美颜系列Q10 滋润活肤霜  100ml', 555, 499, 555, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>产品说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	取自多种生化萃取精华，可防止肌肤粗糙，去除肌肤污垢，预防肌肤暗沉。保持肌肤年轻，让肌肤再现青春亮彩。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<strong>使用说明：</strong>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使<span style="line-height:1.5;">用长效保湿晶露后，取适量均匀涂抹肌肤，使其吸收即可。<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/b/b/f/3/55754c09d43fa.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/f/1/9/3/55754c1169b27.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/4/a/4/6/55754c25574ef.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/5/2/4/55754c37c691a.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/c/3/f/55754c40583c8.jpg" alt="" /></span>\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '保湿、紧致、锁水、除皱', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/e/2/d/d/thumb_55754b5c3981f.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433750607, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(42, 22, 0, 35, 0, 0, 'QQ胶原蛋白皂', 80, 72, 80, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：新果冻质感的洁面皂，触感柔软，可直接用在脸上划圈圈按摩富含胶原蛋白保湿成分，保湿美容液是其他洁面皂的30倍，弱酸性配方，温和不刺激。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：清水温润面部，轻搓手工皂，在面部打圈按摩，再用清水洗净即可。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/4/9/b/55754c510c842.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/d/c/2/55754c663363f.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/a/5/f/55754c72bd26c.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/0/8/9/2/55754c7fe790d.JPG" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '手工皂 香皂', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/6/b/5/8/thumb_55754c1e66542.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433750666, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(43, 22, 0, 35, 0, 0, '金箔皂', 120, 108, 120, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：适合任何肤质，有效抗氧化、抗衰老、修护、保湿、美白、镇静抗皱、减淡细纹\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：清水温润面部，轻搓手工皂，在面部打圈按摩，再用清水洗净即可。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/7/4/1/4/55754e88091d8.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/1/1/6/9/55754e9d4e82f.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/5/9/8/6/55754ea643600.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/5/5/0/e/55754eb0d4b2a.JPG" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '手工皂 香皂', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/6/e/7/8/thumb_55754e5825fcc.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433751220, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(44, 22, 0, 35, 0, 0, '痘痘皂', 120, 108, 120, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：富含茶树精油、活性硫精华，有效摆脱油光，减少粉刺生成，调节油脂，改善肌肤油水失衡，保持肌肤油水平衡，深层保湿补水，舒缓安抚肌肤使肌肤维持健康正常状态。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：清水温润面部，轻搓手工皂，在面部打圈按摩，再用清水洗净即可。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/a/d/1/55754f7f7fcd9.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/6/4/a/7/55754f918bc13.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/5/9/d/55754f9accdd8.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/7/5/6/a/55754fa4a32e1.JPG" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '手工皂 香皂', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/a/c/6/a/thumb_55754f44dd85a.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433751472, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(45, 22, 0, 35, 0, 0, '丝瓜皂', 60, 54, 60, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：天然纤维丝瓜、桂花植物精油、羊毛脂、甘油欧洲进口国际级化妆品染料。有效去除角质、滋润保湿、淡化细纹、加速循环、细致肌肤\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：清水温润面部，轻搓手工皂，在面部打圈按摩，再用清水洗净即可。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/0/d/b/d/557550b8940d3.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/7/b/8/b/557550ca4c120.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/e/b/f/557550d6af99f.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/6/f/c/9/557550deca884.JPG" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '手工皂 香皂', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/c/b/c/thumb_557550497268a.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433751783, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(46, 22, 0, 35, 0, 0, '蜗牛皂', 70, 63, 70, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：如含蜗牛粘液提取物有效改善肤色晦暗，祛痘淡化痘痕，修复受损，控油美白。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：清水温润面部，轻搓手工皂，在面部打圈按摩，再用清水洗净即可。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/9/0/b/5575519b517cd.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/8/0/1/d/557551a4c055e.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/7/e/2/557551abc07fe.JPG" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/f/c/f/8/557551b60d730.JPG" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '手工皂 香皂', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/1/c/a/1/thumb_55755168002d1.JPG', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433752048, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(47, 22, 0, 36, 0, 0, '芷伊蘭美颜系列 硫辛酸紧实霜', 747, 672, 747, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：本品含外用Bio-bustyl多肽可紧实肌肤，琉辛酸维他命，角鲨烷等抗自由基成分可保护细胞之完整性，让疲惫老化之肌肤再现年轻光彩。\n</p>\n<p>\n	使用说明：早晚洁肤、爽(柔)肤后,取适量均匀涂抹脸部及颈部,轻轻由下向上按摩,直至吸收即可。\n</p>\n<p>\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/b/8/0/1/55755879954f3.jpg" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '面霜 ', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/7/f/4/thumb_55755855a3e4f.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433753729, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(48, 22, 0, 37, 0, 0, '芷伊蘭美颜系列 长效保湿晶露', 465, 418, 465, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0in;background-color:#FFFFFF;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<span style="font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;color:#FF0066;font-weight:bold;">产品说明：</span><span style="font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;">含生化萃取精华可长效保湿保护表皮细胞，让肌肤常保健康与滋润。</span><span style="font-size:24px;"><span style="font-family:&apos;microsoft yahei&apos;;"><span style="line-height:1.5;">&nbsp;萃取自纳豆菌发酵产物，具强力含水保湿力，可提高皮肤的天然保湿因子，提高皮肤的含水量与锁水能力，HA玻尿酸强化皮肤锁水保湿功能。MD24促使皮肤细胞充分达到含水保湿之健康与滋润。</span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0in;background-color:#FFFFFF;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0in;background-color:#FFFFFF;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<span style="line-height:36px;font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;color:#FF0066;font-weight:bold;">使用说明：</span><span style="line-height:36px;font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;">每日</span><span style="line-height:36px;font-size:18pt;font-family:calibri;">2-3</span><span style="line-height:36px;font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;">次，取适量均匀涂抹肌肤，使其吸收即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;text-indent:0in;background-color:#FFFFFF;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<span style="line-height:36px;font-size:18pt;font-family:宋体;"><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/9/5/1/55755b84bcc8e.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/e/a/4/55755b90adb66.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/7/3/5/f/55755ba03b83a.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/c/6/a/8/55755bab2c6d2.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/1/9/7/0/55755bb711e8c.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/5/e/3/a/55755bbfeb7c6.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/0/7/c/4/55755bc80e5c2.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/7/d/7/a/55755bd05ac8a.jpg" alt="" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '精华  保湿  ', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/f/9/6/8/thumb_5575597ec3f36.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433754593, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(49, 22, 0, 37, 0, 0, '芷伊蘭美颜系列 神经醯胺修护精华液', 660, 594, 660, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：神经醯胺是近年来开发出的最新一代保湿剂，是一种水溶性脂质物质，他和构成皮肤角质层的物质结构相近，能很快渗透进皮肤和交织成中的水结合，形成一种网状结构，锁住水分。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	使用说明：每日2-3次，取适量均匀涂抹肌肤，使其吸收即可。\n</p>\n<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/c/7/4/b/55755c7687578.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/c/f/1/0/55755c837fea4.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/4/4/c/55755c8e2ff92.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/6/0/0/c/55755c98062a4.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/2/b/3/e/55755ca2529ec.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/d/1/6/4/55755cadc90e2.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/c/8/e/55755cb6bdc04.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/e/e/e/f/55755cc09020c.jpg" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '精华', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/c/f/0/e/thumb_55755c416f9fc.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433754825, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(50, 22, 0, 36, 0, 0, '芷伊蘭美颜系列 亮采防护霜', 375, 337, 375, 0, 10, '<p style="margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;vertical-align:baseline;">\n	产品说明：本品为纯物理性防晒，不含化学性阳光过滤剂，可同时阻挡紫外线UVA及UVB，不含香精并具备防水、防汗及滋润、保湿、强化肌肤防护能力，并防止皮肤干燥之特色。\n</p>\n<p>\n	使用说明：取适量产品在手上，均匀涂抹于面部，颈部以及手部等暴露在阳光下的肌肤，由内向外轻推抹匀即可。注：涂了防晒品，如果不仔细卸妆清洁，就会导致皮肤晦暗缺乏健康光泽，肌肤松弛，滋生暗疮。\n</p>\n<p>\n	<img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/c/9/6/d/55755e18d601f.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/1/6/8/7/55755e22452e7.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/a/e/0/b/55755e2b993c7.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/5/d/5/8/55755e3882879.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/9/5/d/6/55755e442ec52.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/5/2/c/f/55755e4cd6bd2.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/1/4/0/3/55755e72e6887.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/d/5/d/4/55755e7cb143c.jpg" alt="" />\n</p>', 'cohuek1432710740', '面霜  防晒', 0, 'http://www.softphs.com/uploads/c/cohuek1432710740/b/0/3/c/thumb_55755dced126f.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1433755273, 0, 1000, 'float', '30.00', '1', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
